title: Rütavere
text: Rütavere is a village in <a href="Tori%20Parish">Tori Parish</a>, <a href="P%C3%A4rnu%20County">Pärnu County</a> in southwestern <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>. Prior to the administrative reform of Estonian local governments in 2017, the village was part of <a href="Sauga%20Parish">Sauga Parish</a>.
